.login-page
  .alert.alert-success.login-success
    | Welcome back!

  .alert.alert-warning.login-failed
    | The email or password are not valid.

  form.login.col-md-6
    .form-group
      input.form-control(name="email", placeholder="Email")

    .form-group
      input.form-control(name="password", type="password", placeholder="Password")

    .form-group
      button.btn.btn-primary Login
